ollapse\">\n                    <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav navbar-right\">\n                        <!-- ADD MENU LINKS HERE. THESE ARE NON-FUNCTIONAL EXAMPLES. -->\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\">Our Store</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/dealsonlywebstore\">About Us</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://contact.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?ContactUserNextGen&amp;recipient=dealsonlywebstore\">Contact Us</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div>\n                    <div class=\"main-image\">\n                        <img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/18806/AT1102_10_pocket_toolbag_detail_01.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Responsive image\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <h3>Product Details</h3>\n                <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n                <div class=\"product-specs\">\n                    <table>\n                        <tbody>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">MPN:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right\">10TTTBP</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">UPC:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right\">810058484437</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">10 POCKET LEATHER TOOL POUCH: This leather tool pouch can handle any job! It features x4 large front pockets, x1 tape measure holder, x2 hammer holds and x4 narrow pockets, making it a great add on to an existing tool belt for more storage or as a compact tool belt on its own (belt not included)</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">WIDE 3.5 INCH TUNNEL LOOP: The 3.5 inch wide leather tunnel loop on the backside of the tool belt makes it easy to slide on to an existing tool belt to give you more tool storage</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">QUALITY LEATHER TOOL BAG: Made from top grain leather with double rivets and reinforced stitching, this leather tool pouch is made to be used and is of high quality; the tool belt will be stiff upon arrival but will soften and relax with use and time</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">WIDE APPLICATION: This heavy duty tool pouch from ToolTreaux is suitable for DIY at home, construction, electrical work, carpentry, woodworking, framing and building, for plumbers, contractors and more; great gifts for men, Dad gifts, husbands, brothers and boyfriends</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Dimensions: 12 x 10 x 3 inches; Color: Tan Brown; Material: Leather; Weight: 1.60lbs</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>ToolTreaux 10 Pocket Heavy Duty Leather Tool Pouch DIY Woodworking, 12 x 10 Inch</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">64.99</span></h2>\n                <p>Featuring top grain leather fabrication, wide 3.5 inch backside tunnel loop and 10 pockets for additional tool storage, this leather tool pouch is heavy duty, made to be used and can handle any job you throw its way!\n\nThis heavy duty leather tool pouch or tool bag comes with x4 large front pockets (11 x 7, 8 x 5, 9 x 6 and 7.5 x 7 inches), x2 hammer holds (one fixed and one swivel) and x6 smaller thin pockets for pencils, screwdrivers or the like, it can host a lot of tools, a tape measure and more in its generous 12 x 10 inch design. And, made from top grain leather with double rivets and reinforced corner stitching, this leather tool pouch is of high quality and fabricated from quality materials; the tool pouch will be stiff upon arrival but will soften and relax with use and time.\n\nThis heavy duty tool pouch from ToolTreaux has a wide application range! It’s suitable for DIY at home, construction, electrical work, carpentry, woodworking, framing and building, for plumbers, contractors and more; it also makes great gifts for men, Dad gifts, husbands, brothers and boyfriends.\n\nWith ample space for tools, including deep pockets for nail and screws, a tape measure, pencil holders, hammer loops and more, this large capacity tool pouch will give you more than sufficient access to and storage of tools, so you can focus on the job at hand.  \n\nPlease Note: the tool belt is not customizable or able to be personalized</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n                <p>© 2025</p>\n            </div> <!-- /footer -->\n    \n        </div> <!-- /container -->\n        <div style=\"clear:both\">\n            &nbsp;<table></table>\n        </div>\n",
